## ⁉️ More random things

Feel free to add more random things here. Some ideas:

-   Random from a seed
-   Numbers
-   Dates
-   Cities (maybe in cooperation with map modules)
-   Countries (maybe in cooperation with map modules)
-   Flags
-   Random names from more countries
